Based on stolen [[Eriadu/Legends|Eriadu]] designs, the '''Sith power gauntlets''' utilized bursts of [[Repulsorlift/Legends|repulsorlift]] energy to assist movement. They were rarely seen outside of [[Sith/Legends|Sith]] possession during the [[Jedi Civil War]].

